import React from 'react'

const SearchIcon = () => {
    return (
        <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            strokeLinecap="round"
            strokeLinejoin="round"
            strokeWidth="2"
            className="feather feather-search"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        >
            <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"></circle>
            <path d="M21 21L16.65 16.65"></path>
        </svg>
    )
}

export default SearchIcon
